{"tid":1550653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「佐敦之路」聯校人鏈大行動！請廣傳！！！幫推","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T16:08:07.000Z","uid":185425,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7bbb085f40e614fe5e200c6b51e8e0a50f2c0adc","tid":1550653,"uid":185425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"【中學生X大學生 |「佐敦之路」聯校人鏈大行動】<br />\n<br />\n踏入第三個月，抗爭局勢益見嚴峻，連日來的傷亡更是每個心繁家園的香港人不能磨滅的烙印。未來是我們的，香港這家是我們的；青年問題並不是林家鄭氏所稱往內地發展就能解決。莘莘學子，是時候集結力量表態了。<br />\n<br />\n9月9日早上七點開始，佐敦區內的五所學校將舉行聯校人鏈行動，誠邀各位愛港心切的中學生、大學生以及一眾校友街坊一起組織「佐敦之路」，向政權表達學生對五大訴求的堅持。學生可不是區區「動議撤回」四字就能打發走的。五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n活動詳情：<br />\n日期：九月九日（星期一）<br />\n集合時間：早上七時至七時十分<br />\n連結人鏈時間：七時十分至八時<br />\n特別衣著/物資：黑衣、黑口罩、文宣（只作建議）<br />\n※本活動歡迎所有校友舊生參與，請各位師兄師姐多多支持！※<br />\n<br />\n各校集合地點：<br />\n理工大學：紅磡A出口<br />\n嘉諾撒聖瑪利書院：金巴利道校門外<br />\n拔萃女書院：佐敦地鐵站B2出口<br />\n循道中學：加士居道50號<br />\n天主教新民書院：中華書局<br />\n※七時十五分後到達的同學請直接加入人鏈※<br />\n<br />\n理工大學<br />\n嘉諾撒聖瑪利書院<br />\n拔萃女書院<br />\n循道中學<br />\n天主教新民書院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LLVEdfO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLLVEdfO.png&h=17c9346e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xhVHVt9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxhVHVt9.png&h=99ef3340&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMW4pnv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMW4pnv.png&h=a9ad2447&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4Q8Q2w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4Q8Q2w.png&h=df2c0be8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8O1LTfR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8O1LTfR.png&h=f10a793e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"012557bc76b0551a7dbca50cc06f56bca377ce9a","tid":1550653,"uid":185425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:59:59.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"c71f6425cf243b6595a42c4b1a9398b5a0de9bc4","tid":1550653,"uid":185425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:00:09.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"23acd639aab1d73bf3f2230672adcf3e556d4399","tid":1550653,"uid":185425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:00:21.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"99fb184de57cb93ea92f72a56df8a7df07e3229f","tid":1550653,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:00:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2826c5c9e448e5f58e6a76e9c4c7cb568b8f19d9","tid":1550653,"uid":185425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:00:44.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"9796a7ee44dc4c598b0a8b3df41a1a463ea37d89","tid":1550653,"uid":185425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:00:56.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"d71578c626981409c1ac18478fc3da7bbf01585c","tid":1550653,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evxvjtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevxvjtB.jpg&h=73325a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 快啲聽熟加背歌詞，<br />\n唱得莊嚴啲！</span>\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC5hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=23c46c42\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"61fd766f69fcab541cdcaff7fcc6a535ff7e8cdb","tid":1550653,"uid":185425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:12.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"e50ea969f55393cdd364a42629c9e9b211122ccd","tid":1550653,"uid":185425,"like":